00:05:20.110 --> 00:05:21.110
There's no way.

00:05:21.630 --> 00:05:23.670
This barrier was set by Father.

00:05:24.130 --> 00:05:24.909
You can't break it.

00:05:24.910 --> 00:05:25.750
Young Master,

00:05:26.030 --> 00:05:27.230
