00:05:45.470 --> 00:05:46.190
I...

00:05:46.390 --> 00:05:47.470
You talk too much.

00:05:47.750 --> 00:05:49.469
Young Master, don't worry.

00:05:49.470 --> 00:05:51.030
We won't fail you.

00:05:51.230 --> 00:05:51.790
Let's go!

00:05:51.990 --> 00:05:52.830
Bai Lu.

00:05:56.110 --> 00:05:57.790
Don't let Zhilou worry about me.

00:05:58.390 --> 00:05:59.310
Got it.

00:05:59.830 --> 00:06:00.950
We'll keep it quiet.

00:06:01.870 --> 00:06:02.790
Young Master,

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:06.070
