in the sanctuary.

00:06:12.790 --> 00:06:14.309
Miss, does this look cute?

00:06:14.310 --> 00:06:15.029
Does it sound nice?

00:06:15.030 --> 00:06:15.990
So childish.

00:06:17.710 --> 00:06:19.429
Those pastries we bought were amazing!

00:06:19.430 --> 00:06:19.909
Right?

00:06:19.910 --> 00:06:21.830
- Come by my place and try some!
- Sure!

00:06:23.590 --> 00:06:24.550
Xiaoyu,

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:25.869
