00:09:53.190 --> 00:09:54.670
Why would I see one?

00:09:58.230 --> 00:09:59.870
Go to bed now.

00:10:00.670 --> 00:10:01.669
Miss,

00:10:01.670 --> 00:10:03.829
if you end up giving me
a dragon child to play with,

00:10:03.830 --> 00:10:05.469
I'll finally have connections!

00:10:05.470 --> 00:10:07.990
